      <p>The result is solid if not revolutionary. Bragg uses USDA Organic, unfiltered ACV with "the Mother" at the standard 500mg dose, supplemented with vitamin B12. The gummy maintains the brand's commitment to organic sourcing and avoids artificial colors, flavors, and preservatives. The taste is clean and apple-forward, though not quite as refined as Goli's more polished flavor profile.</p>

